title: UGG Australia - The Style Guide Series - Featuring The Dandy
description:
Need a little inspiration? Get a chic peek of how to wear UGG boots with this season's hottest styles. From the best boots to wear with skinny jeans, to working chic skirts with boots, we've got you covered.

THE DANDYLION: Kick your heels up in the Dandylion - a sleek, modern ankle bootie with supreme wearability. Perfect for brunch with the girls.

WEAR WITH:
Work a demure, ladylike look and pair the Dandylion with a knee length A-line skirt. Or unleash your inner downtown darling and style the booties with neutral skinny jeans and a sharp knit.
